Ultimo Campeon followed the Oteybis staff into the Oteybis ship.  
"I am expecting a, what do you say, 'special delivery' that has a 
ETA of 4.567 hours.  I would muchly oblige, if you would sign for it 
and bring it to me as soon as it arrives."  He said to the seven 
members escorting him.
